ZH: 我们不能太沮丧，因为柳暗花明。
EN: We shouldn't be too disheartened, for there is always light at the end of the tunnel.

ZH: 虽然现在很困难，但是柳暗花明，一切会好起来的。
EN: Although things are tough now, there is always a silver lining and things will get better.

ZH: 生活中总是有柳暗花明的时刻。
EN: There are always moments of hope and beauty in life.

ZH: 失去了工作不代表一切结束了，柳暗花明，新的机会会出现。
EN: Losing a job doesn't mean it's the end of everything, there is always light at the end of the tunnel and new opportunities will arise.

ZH: 在黑暗中，总会有光明，柳暗花明。
EN: In darkness, there is always light to be found, a silver lining.

ZH: 无论遇到什么困难，都要记住柳暗花明的道理。
EN: No matter what difficulties we face, always remember that there is light at the end of the tunnel.

ZH: 人生道路上，难免会遇到困难，不要放弃，柳暗花明。
EN: In life, we will inevitably face challenges, but we must not give up, for there is always hope.

ZH: 即使现在陷入困境，也要相信柳暗花明。
EN: Even in times of hardship, believe that there is always light at the end of the tunnel.

